如果細心d聽， 軒仔係好注重咬字， 特別係唱d歌詞好密嘅歌 。<br />\n一般尼講，好明顯軒仔咬字嘅力度係比Eason大好多。 有好有唔好啦，  的確軒仔為左咬準個字會令舌頭唔係最好嘅位置，  呢樣係影響到佢嘅發聲。<br />\n<br />\n唱功尼講，Eason係空氣嘅運用係好出色， 呢樣野軒仔好明顯係比下去。<br />\n<br />\n不過Eason係低至中音區係最靚聲， 因為佢本身嘅chest voice(姐係平時講野個把聲)好靚。<br />\n而軒仔最强嘅地方係C4以上， 開始要Mix啲假音落去嘅時候， 佢控制Chest voice同假音嘅比例係好好，所以無論佢可以好溫柔咁唱個d音，又可以好強好powerful咁唱，令到首歌好有層次。<br />\n<br />\n真假音轉換我諗都唔使講，呢樣野可以話係軒仔最西利嘅野。<br />\nEason同軒仔勁嘅地方都唔同，我個人兩個都好鍾意，聽佢地嘅歌大好幸福!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c673e6bd82ccc712e7840bc166ea26b89e7f1d7","tid":829513,"uid":79389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"hins同eason同林子祥其實有過合唱大家記唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n當年睇電視直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過youtube搵唔番<br />\n好似三爺孫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av9501984/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav9501984%2F&d=nD3x63jW2otb9wdOfdZtF54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b6e14ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av9501984/</a><br />\n<br />\n然後hins 同 eason ge合唱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yjL1ZGaQEE8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyjL1ZGaQEE8&d=nD3x63jW2otb9wdOfdZtF54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8ef4e82f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yjL1ZGaQEE8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZlX8dgHzpzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZlX8dgHzpzU&d=nD3x63jW2otb9wdOfdZtF54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=93c5f1f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZlX8dgHzpzU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: eason死忠, 軒仔fans"},{"pid":"c3b16ab158c200d3d4b8cdbd0ee73c18ef0e8790","tid":829513,"uid":198289,